{"tid":1463054,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實林鄭有無諗過， 如果有成1萬，甚至十萬既人","createTime":"2019-08-13T11:59:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-13T18:05:07.000Z","uid":193768,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"c40ae1f40a5eadde09372708889f0fb02e47e6b7","tid":1463054,"uid":193768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T11:59:01.000Z","msg":"其實林鄭有無諗過， 如果有成1萬，甚至十萬既人都唔怕因為非法集中而俾人拉既人， 咁點搞好？<br />\n<br />\n佢依家成日都話行動係針對啲放火，彈珠等等既人所以咁武力， 就算拉晒啲好激進既人，都唔代表其他無咁武力既人唔會出黎<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有成十萬人唔怕俾人拉， 咁香港係咪真係可以承受到呢個創傷？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁大個政府機構， 咁多議員， 真係一個方法都諗唔到咁可悲咩？？？"},{"pid":"ae361afbcc749d8f1c17185c8f4c3ab42f5dc000","tid":1463054,"uid":193768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:02:48.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c99a49afba89ddd23876fbd9c4fc5cf44a19c048","tid":1463054,"uid":258598,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:03:22.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"46134228f35e13222e16f720efe29c176c6630f9","tid":1463054,"uid":74058,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:05:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果有1萬人索帶麻包袋<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />高官、黑警<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4fcf53c17ee780471d5e20d267e87fe994688bad","tid":1463054,"uid":121546,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:08:54.000Z","msg":"中國大把人口可以換落黎<br />\n消極自殘既策略係香港行唔通"},{"pid":"bf8ba2a31e829f9fc7dce8bddfb712ecf081fbd4","tid":1463054,"uid":193768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:09:30.000Z","msg":"而係， 知唔知咁多人要拉幾耐？<br />\n<br />\n如果真係有咁多， 點搞好"},{"pid":"cbc43f03408e17b108915826cd51e323df938a43","tid":1463054,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf8ba2a31e829f9fc7dce8bddfb712ecf081fbd4","tid":1463054,"uid":193768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-13T12:09:30.000